WEBVTT

00:00:35.933 --> 00:00:38.933
=Angels and Guards=

00:00:38.966 --> 00:00:41.200
=Episode 25=

00:00:45.566 --> 00:00:46.333
Guokai.

00:00:47.000 --> 00:00:49.500
You commanded last night's operation?

00:00:50.033 --> 00:00:51.033
Yes, my lord.

00:00:51.266 --> 00:00:54.166
I will be sure to recommend you
for a reward.

00:00:55.233 --> 00:00:56.500
Thank you, my lord.

00:00:59.500 --> 00:01:00.400
And Feng Fuliu?

00:01:01.433 --> 00:01:02.633
The phantom thief Feng Fuliu

00:01:02.833 --> 00:01:03.933
knew he had no way out,

00:01:03.933 --> 00:01:06.433
so he threw himself into the fire
and burned to ashes.

00:01:07.666 --> 00:01:08.500
He is dead?

00:01:10.600 --> 00:01:11.433
What a pity.

00:01:12.233 --> 00:01:13.666
He was a master of his time,

00:01:14.200 --> 00:01:15.533
brilliant beyond compare.

00:01:17.366 --> 00:01:17.966
Guokai.

00:01:18.433 --> 00:01:19.266
You worked hard.

00:01:19.433 --> 00:01:20.333
Go get some rest.

00:01:21.033 --> 00:01:22.700
Then I shall take my leave.

00:01:25.433 --> 00:01:28.133
Rest assured. I will recommend you
for credit.

00:01:28.766 --> 00:01:29.466
Thank you, my lord.

00:01:33.666 --> 00:01:34.033
Yes.

00:01:43.666 --> 00:01:44.266
What a pity.

00:01:46.600 --> 00:01:47.366
Feng Fuliu.

00:01:48.333 --> 00:01:50.933
Why did you insist on hunting Leng Xin?

00:01:51.900 --> 00:01:54.166
That is what got you killed.

00:01:55.733 --> 00:01:56.900
You are the first person

00:01:57.400 --> 00:01:58.433
who has dared, right in front of me,

00:01:59.566 --> 00:02:02.500
to hit and scold my son.

00:02:04.500 --> 00:02:05.200
My Lady.

00:02:05.866 --> 00:02:06.433
Good.

00:02:07.566 --> 00:02:08.466
That brat

00:02:08.900 --> 00:02:10.666
needs someone who can keep him in line.

00:02:12.600 --> 00:02:13.633
He used to fear me.

00:02:14.100 --> 00:02:14.800
Now,

00:02:17.233 --> 00:02:18.466
it seems he fears you a little.

00:02:20.100 --> 00:02:20.933
No, no.

00:02:21.533 --> 00:02:22.033
We...

00:02:22.333 --> 00:02:23.500
Neither of us fears the other.

00:02:23.700 --> 00:02:24.466
That won't do.

00:02:25.066 --> 00:02:26.300
You need to make him fear you.

00:02:27.000 --> 00:02:27.566
Otherwise,

00:02:27.866 --> 00:02:29.300
he will be hard to handle in the future.

00:02:31.166 --> 00:02:31.900
In the future?

00:02:32.833 --> 00:02:33.433
Handle?

00:02:34.866 --> 00:02:35.466
Handle what?

00:02:37.500 --> 00:02:38.233
Handle whom?

00:02:39.333 --> 00:02:40.500
Girl,

00:02:41.066 --> 00:02:42.500
you really are interesting.

00:02:51.266 --> 00:02:52.433
Straightforward.

00:02:53.033 --> 00:02:53.566
You're indeed

00:02:53.900 --> 00:02:54.966
quite unique.

00:03:01.333 --> 00:03:03.566
No wonder that brat cares about you.

00:03:04.766 --> 00:03:05.166
I...

00:03:05.233 --> 00:03:05.766
That's not true.

00:03:06.400 --> 00:03:08.233
Good. Very good.

00:03:11.333 --> 00:03:12.500
Mother, take care.

00:03:14.866 --> 00:03:16.233
You little scoundrel.

00:03:16.933 --> 00:03:19.000
You do have good taste in women.

00:03:20.666 --> 00:03:22.066
I chose one after your example.

00:03:22.733 --> 00:03:24.266
Smooth talker. I'm leaving.

00:03:34.866 --> 00:03:35.566
Go back.

00:04:13.833 --> 00:04:16.100
What was all that crying
and shouting just now?

00:04:18.533 --> 00:04:19.900
So you really are not Feng Fuliu.

00:04:20.533 --> 00:04:22.766
I was never Feng Fuliu.

00:04:34.733 --> 00:04:36.100
You thought I was Feng Fuliu

00:04:36.400 --> 00:04:37.166
and feared something had happened to me?

00:04:44.533 --> 00:04:46.533
Then were you worried

00:04:47.766 --> 00:04:50.300
about me, or about Feng Fuliu?

00:04:57.833 --> 00:04:58.900
Then why

00:05:00.933 --> 00:05:02.500
did Leng Xin try to kill Feng Fuliu?

00:05:03.733 --> 00:05:04.266
It may

00:05:04.700 --> 00:05:05.866
also have something to do with the jade.

00:05:07.533 --> 00:05:10.900
It seems he couldn't wait any longer.

00:05:12.733 --> 00:05:14.000
You mean

00:05:14.533 --> 00:05:16.433
Feng Fuliu has been stealing treasures

00:05:16.733 --> 00:05:17.933
to investigate Leng Xin?

00:05:18.033 --> 00:05:20.433
That jade is no ordinary object.

00:05:20.833 --> 00:05:22.533
Only imperial relatives and nobles

00:05:22.733 --> 00:05:23.500
who rendered great service
could have one.

00:05:24.233 --> 00:05:24.933
So,

00:05:26.233 --> 00:05:26.800
Leng Xin

00:05:27.933 --> 00:05:29.433
can't be from common origins.

00:05:32.533 --> 00:05:34.866
Then that means Leng Xin

00:05:35.166 --> 00:05:37.100
is an assassin kept

00:05:37.333 --> 00:05:38.333
by some powerful court official.

00:05:39.600 --> 00:05:40.333
Very likely.

00:05:42.766 --> 00:05:45.333
Why would this powerful official
do such a thing?

00:05:47.333 --> 00:05:48.333
To eliminate rivals.

00:05:49.166 --> 00:05:49.900
Young Master.

00:05:50.400 --> 00:05:50.966
Young Master.

00:05:52.200 --> 00:05:53.533
Chief Squad Leader Hua
and Squad Leader Cheng are back.

00:06:08.066 --> 00:06:08.833
Hua.

00:06:09.433 --> 00:06:10.633
What happened?

00:06:10.666 --> 00:06:11.766
Where did Leng Xin go?

00:06:12.933 --> 00:06:13.600
Hua.

00:06:14.066 --> 00:06:14.733
Did you find any clues

00:06:14.733 --> 00:06:15.633
while tracking Leng Xin?

00:06:17.500 --> 00:06:18.266
He...

00:06:18.733 --> 00:06:21.166
He fled to a residence
in the western city.

00:06:21.666 --> 00:06:22.666
It was too dark.

00:06:23.900 --> 00:06:25.400
I couldn't see clearly.

00:06:26.066 --> 00:06:27.233
Was there no plaque at the gate?

00:06:27.533 --> 00:06:28.966
That is the strange part.

00:06:29.566 --> 00:06:30.933
There was no plaque at the gate.

00:06:31.866 --> 00:06:33.400
But I marked the entrance.

00:06:33.533 --> 00:06:34.866
We should find it
if we search carefully.

00:06:36.833 --> 00:06:38.333
Leng Xin is badly wounded now.

00:06:38.766 --> 00:06:41.133
We should use this chance
to drag him out.

00:06:41.866 --> 00:06:43.066
What about Feng Fuliu?

00:06:43.866 --> 00:06:45.466
He can't really be dead, can he?

00:06:53.066 --> 00:06:55.266
If the Young Duke is safe and sound,

00:06:55.933 --> 00:06:56.866
then Feng Fuliu

00:06:58.000 --> 00:06:59.366
may not have been so lucky.

00:07:00.566 --> 00:07:01.566
Seriously?

00:07:02.400 --> 00:07:03.833
Why do you keep linking

00:07:03.866 --> 00:07:05.433
Feng Fuliu to me?

00:07:06.533 --> 00:07:07.433
Don't worry, Young Master Chang.

00:07:07.766 --> 00:07:08.533
From today on,

00:07:09.366 --> 00:07:11.400
no one will link you two together again.

00:07:23.166 --> 00:07:23.900
Guokai. Good news.

00:07:24.566 --> 00:07:27.233
In the matter of killing Feng Fuliu,

00:07:27.833 --> 00:07:29.433
you have made a great contribution.

00:07:30.366 --> 00:07:31.200
The Cabinet

00:07:31.733 --> 00:07:35.066
reported it to His Majesty,
and he was greatly pleased.

00:07:36.100 --> 00:07:36.666
Look.

00:07:37.333 --> 00:07:40.000
His Majesty has awarded you a jade belt

00:07:40.400 --> 00:07:41.466
as encouragement.

00:07:51.766 --> 00:07:53.100
Long live His Majesty!

00:07:53.866 --> 00:07:54.633
Thank His Majesty!

00:07:54.833 --> 00:07:55.933
Keep it up!

00:07:56.666 --> 00:07:57.833
Thank you, my lord.

00:07:58.433 --> 00:07:59.133
The Cabinet

00:07:59.166 --> 00:08:00.600
has recorded your achievement

00:08:01.066 --> 00:08:02.966
as a three-level merit.

00:08:03.333 --> 00:08:06.433
I believe at the year-end
official review,

00:08:06.933 --> 00:08:08.833
a promotion will surely be yours.

00:08:09.500 --> 00:08:11.233
It is all thanks to your support,
my lord.

00:08:12.200 --> 00:08:13.133
Not at all.

00:08:15.000 --> 00:08:15.700
Duoyu.

00:08:16.766 --> 00:08:17.966
Greetings, Commander.

00:08:18.266 --> 00:08:18.700
Commissioner Lu.

00:08:19.033 --> 00:08:20.466
Duoyu

00:08:20.866 --> 00:08:22.633
helped greatly in capturing Diaotu,

00:08:23.033 --> 00:08:24.566
going to Liao,
and catching Feng Fuliu.

00:08:25.033 --> 00:08:26.433
He has done much to assist us.

00:08:27.400 --> 00:08:28.233
I have decided

00:08:29.533 --> 00:08:31.633
to make an exception and promote him

00:08:32.200 --> 00:08:33.466
to Jinyiwei Squad Leader.

00:08:41.666 --> 00:08:42.233
Thank you

00:08:42.566 --> 00:08:44.100
for this great grace, Commander.

00:08:52.233 --> 00:08:53.833
(Just because of this scrap of cloth,)

00:08:54.566 --> 00:08:57.133
(you are certain Feng Fuliu is dead?)

00:08:57.733 --> 00:08:59.133
(What do you mean?)

00:08:59.333 --> 00:09:00.766
(Can you prove he is alive?)

00:09:01.233 --> 00:09:01.500
(Well...)

00:09:06.666 --> 00:09:08.666
(Could His Majesty be behind this?)

00:09:12.166 --> 00:09:12.733
Cheers!

00:09:12.733 --> 00:09:13.433
Let me fill you up.

00:09:13.433 --> 00:09:13.866
Okay.

00:09:14.233 --> 00:09:15.233
Fill it up?

00:09:16.266 --> 00:09:17.300
I'm not in a good state.

00:09:17.366 --> 00:09:18.466
Come on. You drink too little.

00:09:18.500 --> 00:09:19.100
Young Master Chang.

00:09:19.100 --> 00:09:19.633
Who are you talking about?

00:09:19.666 --> 00:09:21.000
Your arm is wrapped in gauze.
What happened?

00:09:21.166 --> 00:09:23.066
- You look drunk already.
- Not true. Go on.

00:09:23.266 --> 00:09:24.466
I fell off a horse recently.

00:09:26.266 --> 00:09:26.933
A fall?

00:09:27.600 --> 00:09:28.333
I don't believe it.

00:09:28.500 --> 00:09:29.400
It is a burn, isn't it?

00:09:29.866 --> 00:09:31.033
Go on. Constable Guan.

00:09:31.166 --> 00:09:31.866
Yes. Come on.

00:09:31.866 --> 00:09:33.566
Hua. Are you drunk already?

00:09:33.700 --> 00:09:34.700
This wine is not even strong.

00:09:34.766 --> 00:09:35.800
Maybe a little.

00:09:36.366 --> 00:09:36.766
I'll have more.

00:09:38.233 --> 00:09:39.066
Fill it up.

00:09:40.666 --> 00:09:42.900
- Fill it up.
- I will drink it all.

00:09:43.233 --> 00:09:43.966
Cheers.

00:09:45.066 --> 00:09:45.800
(Feng Fuliu.)

00:09:46.833 --> 00:09:47.933
(Did you really die?)

00:10:01.166 --> 00:10:01.733
Who is there?

00:10:18.233 --> 00:10:19.333
Duoyu.

00:10:21.900 --> 00:10:23.333
Hua. The commander

00:10:23.733 --> 00:10:25.433
finally made an exception
and let me join the Northern Bureau.

00:10:29.866 --> 00:10:30.566
Very good.

00:10:31.600 --> 00:10:32.300
You look sharp.

00:10:36.533 --> 00:10:37.366
Hua.

00:10:38.200 --> 00:10:38.966
I came

00:10:39.000 --> 00:10:39.600
because

00:10:40.200 --> 00:10:41.133
I wanted to thank you.

00:10:41.766 --> 00:10:43.000
For what?

00:10:49.666 --> 00:10:50.666
You gave me courage.

00:10:51.933 --> 00:10:52.933
Thank you for staying by my side.

00:10:59.833 --> 00:11:00.700
Well,

00:11:01.266 --> 00:11:03.466
I'm not as wonderful
as you make me sound.

00:11:04.733 --> 00:11:07.266
Hua, do I look good in this?

00:11:08.333 --> 00:11:09.100
Yes.

00:11:10.666 --> 00:11:11.766
You look wonderful.

00:11:13.833 --> 00:11:15.033
Don't just stand here.

00:11:15.233 --> 00:11:16.233
Come on. Food is on me.

00:11:16.566 --> 00:11:18.233
We should celebrate properly.

00:11:44.733 --> 00:11:45.500
Hua.

00:11:45.866 --> 00:11:47.400
When you said it's your treat,

00:11:48.200 --> 00:11:50.133
you meant tofu pudding
and fried dough sticks?

00:11:51.766 --> 00:11:54.433
You are a seventh-rank Squad Leader.
Why so picky?

00:11:55.200 --> 00:11:56.733
When you make Baihu or Qianhu,

00:11:56.833 --> 00:11:58.066
I will treat you to a real feast.

00:11:58.066 --> 00:11:58.300
Look.

00:11:58.333 --> 00:11:58.833
All right.

00:11:59.266 --> 00:12:00.533
Even Jinyiwei eat at street stalls.

00:12:00.566 --> 00:12:01.766
When I make Baihu or Qianhu,

00:12:02.400 --> 00:12:03.400
I will treat you instead.

00:12:03.400 --> 00:12:03.733
Go, go.

00:12:04.766 --> 00:12:05.433
Eat up.

00:12:12.666 --> 00:12:13.433
Duoyu.

00:12:14.700 --> 00:12:15.766
Do you think Feng Fuliu

00:12:16.233 --> 00:12:16.966
is really dead?

00:12:17.866 --> 00:12:19.133
I doubt it.

00:12:19.833 --> 00:12:21.333
Even Leng Xin escaped.

00:12:21.600 --> 00:12:23.500
Feng Fuliu has the best footwork
in the martial world.

00:12:23.866 --> 00:12:25.766
Would he really do worse than Leng Xin?

00:12:28.933 --> 00:12:30.200
I have my doubts too.

00:12:31.200 --> 00:12:31.900
But

00:12:32.500 --> 00:12:34.400
to the public,

00:12:34.566 --> 00:12:35.766
we say Feng Fuliu is dead.

00:12:37.100 --> 00:12:38.833
Don't worry, Hua. I know what to do.

00:12:39.500 --> 00:12:42.733
I mean, not just at the Northern Bureau.

00:12:43.533 --> 00:12:44.400
At Chong'er Pavilion,

00:12:44.866 --> 00:12:46.233
you must keep your mouth shut too.

00:13:01.400 --> 00:13:02.333
That girl

00:13:03.000 --> 00:13:04.233
always gets stuck in her own head.

00:13:05.600 --> 00:13:08.000
Leng Xin has killed people
in front of her several times.

00:13:08.400 --> 00:13:10.933
Her old hatred has not faded,
and there is fresh blood on top of it.

00:13:11.266 --> 00:13:13.366
So be very careful.

00:13:13.933 --> 00:13:15.633
Don't say anything reckless
in front of her.

00:13:17.400 --> 00:13:18.333
I understand, Hua.

00:13:25.433 --> 00:13:26.600
What is she doing?

00:13:28.266 --> 00:13:29.033
Her?

00:13:30.533 --> 00:13:32.233
She wants to avenge Feng Fuliu.

00:13:40.000 --> 00:13:41.100
Even if you want to catch Leng Xin,

00:13:41.366 --> 00:13:43.100
you don't have to be so hard
on yourself.

00:13:43.500 --> 00:13:45.233
Eat something and rest for a while.

00:13:45.233 --> 00:13:45.966
Chang Beiming.

00:13:46.400 --> 00:13:47.633
Why are you investigating Leng Xin?

00:13:50.033 --> 00:13:51.400
Why am I?

00:13:52.233 --> 00:13:54.000
The files you have on Leng Xin

00:13:54.400 --> 00:13:55.966
are even more complete
than the Northern Bureau's.

00:13:57.066 --> 00:13:58.000
By all accounts,

00:13:59.233 --> 00:14:01.433
you are a young lord who claims
to live free of court affairs.

00:14:02.700 --> 00:14:03.866
So why do you have

00:14:03.866 --> 00:14:05.300
so many case files on Leng Xin?

00:14:07.100 --> 00:14:08.200
I was just

00:14:09.533 --> 00:14:10.266
curious.

00:14:15.866 --> 00:14:16.400
Beiming.

00:14:17.400 --> 00:14:19.633
I wish you would stop
hiding everything from me.

00:14:20.033 --> 00:14:21.233
I'm begging you.

00:14:22.000 --> 00:14:23.033
I want to avenge my father.

00:14:23.833 --> 00:14:25.500
I want to avenge Yuanrong for Xintian.

00:14:26.333 --> 00:14:27.333
For Feng Fuliu,

00:14:27.833 --> 00:14:28.700
and for everyone

00:14:28.700 --> 00:14:29.966
who died under Leng Xin's blade.

00:14:31.333 --> 00:14:32.366
Please.

00:14:32.566 --> 00:14:33.500
Tell me the truth.

00:14:37.100 --> 00:14:37.600
Get up.

00:14:37.600 --> 00:14:38.633
Not until you tell me the truth.

00:14:39.033 --> 00:14:39.766
Fine, I will.

00:14:40.766 --> 00:14:41.766
I don't want you to misunderstand me.

00:14:42.100 --> 00:14:42.833
I will tell you everything.

00:14:49.066 --> 00:14:50.400
I was acting under orders

00:14:51.400 --> 00:14:53.933
to investigate the truth
behind Prince Luo's case in secret.

00:14:55.200 --> 00:14:56.700
The case that got my father killed?

00:14:56.933 --> 00:14:57.533
Yes.

00:14:58.533 --> 00:14:59.233
Orders?

00:15:00.900 --> 00:15:02.833
Who could possibly give you orders?

00:15:03.333 --> 00:15:03.733
Could it be...

00:15:05.000 --> 00:15:06.400
Don't say those words.

00:15:06.533 --> 00:15:07.933
That would be deceiving the Emperor.

00:15:10.566 --> 00:15:11.100
Okay.

00:15:11.933 --> 00:15:12.600
Then,

00:15:13.233 --> 00:15:14.666
did the person who gave yo those orders

00:15:15.200 --> 00:15:17.066
say why the old case had to be reopened?

00:15:17.066 --> 00:15:17.833
Because Prince Luo's case

00:15:18.933 --> 00:15:20.366
involves the Crown Prince and Prince Fu.

00:15:22.433 --> 00:15:24.133
It was only sealed in name.

00:15:24.433 --> 00:15:25.533
I have been investigating it in secret.

00:15:27.166 --> 00:15:28.166
The Crown Prince

00:15:28.866 --> 00:15:29.900
and Prince Fu?

00:15:32.266 --> 00:15:33.100
Don't ask any more.

00:15:33.666 --> 00:15:34.733
If I say anything else,

00:15:35.000 --> 00:15:36.266
I will be guilty
of deceiving the Emperor too.

00:15:39.900 --> 00:15:42.233
Then are you Feng Fuliu or not?

00:15:47.366 --> 00:15:47.966
How are you

00:15:48.600 --> 00:15:50.666
still stuck on that?

00:15:50.933 --> 00:15:52.600
Because I hate being lied to.

00:15:53.400 --> 00:15:54.166
Chang Beiming.

00:15:54.766 --> 00:15:57.700
If you had no choice but to pretend
to be Feng Fuliu,

00:15:58.233 --> 00:15:59.500
then tell me the truth.

00:15:59.733 --> 00:16:01.166
I will choose to believe you.

00:16:01.400 --> 00:16:02.400
But if you are not him,

00:16:03.166 --> 00:16:04.333
tell me that too, please.

00:16:04.866 --> 00:16:06.900
Because I truly hate being deceived.

00:16:12.333 --> 00:16:12.933
Miss Shen!

00:16:15.566 --> 00:16:16.500
Feng Fuliu.

00:16:18.033 --> 00:16:19.100
You really are not Feng Fuliu.

00:16:33.600 --> 00:16:34.166
Feng Fuliu.

00:16:34.733 --> 00:16:35.266
Come out!

00:16:35.666 --> 00:16:36.533
I have questions for you.

00:16:37.400 --> 00:16:38.466
Baihu Shen,

00:16:39.166 --> 00:16:40.600
I'm honored you grieved
so deeply for me.

00:16:41.433 --> 00:16:42.300
I'm most grateful.

00:16:42.833 --> 00:16:43.566
So I came to pay you a visit.

00:16:50.066 --> 00:16:52.600
(Feng Fuliu, you really are alive.)

00:16:54.366 --> 00:16:55.800
(But who exactly are you?)

00:17:02.433 --> 00:17:03.166
Where is Feng Fuliu?

00:17:05.866 --> 00:17:07.133
Feng Fuliu really is not dead.

00:17:07.600 --> 00:17:08.266
I told you.

00:17:09.066 --> 00:17:10.800
If a monster like Leng Xin survived,

00:17:11.033 --> 00:17:12.033
then Feng Fuliu must be fine too.

00:17:12.900 --> 00:17:13.600
But

00:17:14.333 --> 00:17:15.500
who is he?

00:17:17.533 --> 00:17:18.400
He is probably

00:17:19.100 --> 00:17:19.866
a righteous man

00:17:20.566 --> 00:17:21.633
who helps those in need

00:17:22.400 --> 00:17:23.266
in the martial world.

00:17:24.666 --> 00:17:25.266
No.

00:17:26.533 --> 00:17:28.400
His scent was strangely familiar.

00:17:31.900 --> 00:17:33.100
Just now,

00:17:33.400 --> 00:17:35.266
I was standing right in front of you.

00:17:35.766 --> 00:17:37.000
You can't still suspect me.

00:17:39.200 --> 00:17:39.733
I don't.

00:17:41.000 --> 00:17:41.666
But tonight,

00:17:43.100 --> 00:17:44.466
I proved two things.

00:17:46.600 --> 00:17:47.200
Which two?

00:17:48.500 --> 00:17:50.500
First, you are not Feng Fuliu.

00:17:51.533 --> 00:17:52.233
Second...

00:17:53.666 --> 00:17:54.366
What is it?

00:17:55.900 --> 00:17:56.766
The second thing...

00:17:57.333 --> 00:17:58.200
I can't tell you.

00:17:58.566 --> 00:17:59.400
Tell me.

00:18:01.600 --> 00:18:02.366
Tell me.

00:18:07.533 --> 00:18:08.133
Come on.

00:18:27.766 --> 00:18:28.433
Yong Master Chang.

00:18:29.033 --> 00:18:30.800
Your voice-changing pill really works.

00:18:47.133 --> 00:18:50.300
♪Because you once entered my dreams♪

00:18:50.666 --> 00:18:54.033
♪Truth and illusion blur in wine♪

00:18:54.300 --> 00:18:57.300
♪My heart drifted lost♪

00:18:57.300 --> 00:19:00.700
♪Yet found you in the crowd♪

00:19:01.800 --> 00:19:05.000
♪My blood still burns
as the world surges♪

00:19:05.400 --> 00:19:08.733
♪The land is fair, and you are free♪

00:19:09.333 --> 00:19:11.533
♪Sword drawn, lost in obsession♪

00:19:11.533 --> 00:19:15.566
♪I've softly let it go♪

00:19:15.600 --> 00:19:19.466
♪The vow you made was true♪

00:19:19.466 --> 00:19:23.200
♪Yet like clouds, it stops for no one♪

00:19:23.500 --> 00:19:25.400
♪Put away those dreamlike words♪

00:19:25.400 --> 00:19:29.933
♪And forget at world's end♪

00:19:30.266 --> 00:19:31.766
♪Embracing memory♪

00:19:31.766 --> 00:19:34.133
♪Through blossoms and dreams♪

00:19:34.133 --> 00:19:38.000
♪You hide in the crowd, silent♪

00:19:38.000 --> 00:19:40.300
♪I wish to let it pass♪

00:19:40.333 --> 00:19:45.333
♪And run toward this vast life♪